  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM2.3">
<l>ēṟaṭarttatu mēṉamāynilaṅ kīṇṭatummuṉṉi rāmaṉāy</l>
<l>māṟaṭarttatum maṇṇaḷantatuñ collippāṭi vaṇpoṉṉippēr</l>
<l>āṟupōlvaruṅ kaṇṇanīrkoṇṭa raṅkaṉkōyiṟ ṟirumuṟṟam</l>
<l>cēṟuceytoṇṭar cēvaṭicceḻuñ cēṟeṉceṉṉik kaṇivaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I shall wear on my head the abundant slush from the red feet of the devotees</l>
<l>who make slush in the holy courtyard of Raṅga’s temple</l>
<l>with the tears of [their] eyes that stream like the mighty river of bounteous Poṉṉi,</l>
<l>having sung, repeating</l>
<l rend="indent">[His] killing the bulls, [His] splitting off the earth as a boar</l>
<l rend="indent">[His] previously killing the enemies as Rāma, and [His] measuring the earth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
